OL,7,FWater companies have been warned they
OL,8,Fmust prepare now for another severe
OL,9,Fheatwave and drought this summer or
OL,10,Fput millions of customers at risk of
OL,11,Fhosepipe bans.
OL,13,FThe Government's National Drought
OL,14,FGroup, consisting of ministers, the
OL,15,FEnvironment Agency, Met Office, water
OL,16,Fcompanies and farmers, met on
OL,17,FWednesday to discuss the threat to
OL,18,Fsupplies from "continual shocks and
OL,19,Ferratic weather patterns" caused by
OL,20,Fclimate change.
OL,3,CSevere drought this summer could lead
OL,4,Cto more hosepipe bans, water firms
OL,5,Cwarned
